                            <h2 style="color: #00739c;font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;, &quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;font-weight: normal;padding: 0;margin: 0;text-align: left;line-height: 1.3;word-break: normal;font-size: 36px;"><b>Hello Dorian-Vasco,</b>
                            </h2>
							<br>
							
							
							
                            Many clients have asked for a way to give talents feedback on their auditions. Not only to help them improve their work but also to show some appreciation for the effort a talent makes to produce custom demos.<br />
<br />
Sure enough, we also know: Hardly anybody has the time to write a personal note to each and every talent that auditioned for your job.  This is well understood by talents.<br />
<br />
So bodalgo has come up with the <b>fastest way possible to give personal feedback</b> when you feel you want to. Be it because you just want to say "Thanks", be it to draw the talent's attention to a quality issue you might have had with their recording. From today on, giving feedback is as easy as a mouse click.<br />
<br />
Next to every audition, you will find a drop-down menu labeled "Feedback" from which you may select from prewritten feedback options. For you, it is just a click but for the talent, it is valuable information and highly appreciated.<br />
<br />
Try it out next time you post a job on bodalgo!
                          </td>
